Color Thief Changelog
=====================


Version 0.1
-----------

First public preview release.


Version 0.2
-----------

Released on Oct 14th 2015

- Added Python3.x support

Version 0.2.1
-------------

Released on Feb 9th 2017

- Removed useless list creation


Version 1.0
-------------

Released on May 13th 2023

- Added type annotations to colorthief.py. Yield 200% speedboost when installed with mypyc. 
- Updated project to pyproject.toml with mypyc builds.
